title: Little Fish: Bizarre Choreography, Schnapps, and Singing in Swedish
content: Dan, James and Andy discuss YOUR facts including 4D and D-Day. Andy's pronunciation of Houston gets him in trouble again, and we meet eight new Custodians of Fish Facts.
